quran[4]{c,v,t}:
  2,58,"aur jab hum ne ( un se ) kaha ke is gaon mein daakhil ho jao aur is mein jahan se chaho, khoob khao ( piyo ) aur ( dekhna ) darwazay mein daakhil hona to sajda karna aur hittah kehna, hum tumahray gunah maaf kar den ge aur neki karne walon ko aur ziyada den ge"
  2,59,"to jo zalim they, unhon ne is lafz ko, jis ka un ko hukum diya tha, badal kar is ki jagah aur lafz kehna shurukiya, pas hum ne ( un ) zaalmon par aasman se azaab nazilkiya, kyunkay nafarmaniyan kiye jatay they"
  2,60,"aur jab moose ne apni qoum ke liye ( khuda se ) pani manga to hum ne kaha ke apni laathi pathar par maro. ( unhon ne laathi maari ) to phir is mein se baara chashmay phoot niklay, aur tamam logon ne apna apna ghaat maloom kar ( ke pani pi ) liya. ( hum ne hukum diya ke ) khuda ki ( ataa farmai hui ) rozi khao aur piyo, magar zameen mein fasaad nah karte phirna"
  2,61,"aur jab tum ne kaha ke moose! hum se aik ( hi ) khanay par sabr nahi ho sakta to apne perwar-digaar se dua kijiyej ke tarkari aur kakri aur gheehon aur msor aur pyaaz ( waghera ) jo nabataat zameen se ugti hain, hamaray liye peda kar day. unhon ne kaha ke bhala umdah cheeze chore kar un ke aiwz naaqis cheeze kyun chahtay hon. ( agar yahi cheeze matloob hain ) to kisi shehar mein ja uttro, wahan jo mangte ho, mil jaye ga. aur ( aakhir kaar ) zillat ( wa ruswai ) aur mohtaji ( wabay nawai ) un se chimta di gayi aur woh allah ke ghazab mein girftar ho gay. yeh is liye ke woh allah ki aayton se inkaar karte they aur ( is ke ) nabiyo ko na-haq qatal kar dete they. ( yani ) yeh is liye ke nafarmani kiye jatay aur hadd se barhay jatay they"
